## Build artifacts — authoritative build tree lives at ~/esp/brushlesslamp-s3/
## (no spaces, workaround for libsodium's unquoted -include). Same pattern as
## ../esp-idf/.gitignore.
**/build/
**/managed_components/
**/dependencies.lock
**/sdkconfig
**/sdkconfig.old

## clangd index cache
**/.cache/

## OTA / secure-boot signing keys — NEVER commit (private root of trust for
## signed OTA; losing it blocks future updates, leaking it lets anyone sign).
**/ota_signing_key.pem
**/*_signing_key.pem
**/secure_boot_signing_key.pem
